OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,FThe Montane Winter Spine is regarded
OL,7,Fby many as Britain's most brutal
OL,8,Fendurance race.
OL,10,FThe 268-mile race starts in Edale in
OL,11,FDerbyshire and finishes in the village
OL,12,Fof Kirk Yetholm in the Scottish
OL,13,FBorders.
OL,15,FRunners have a time limit of just 168
OL,16,Fhours - or one week - to complete the
OL,17,Fgruelling trail that spans the Pennine
OL,18,FWay.
