OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,FThe winter race has been held annually
OL,7,Fsince 2012 - when only fifteen
OL,8,Fcompetitors met at the start line and
OL,9,Fjust three of them made it to the
OL,10,Ffinish at the Border Hotel wall.
OL,12,FIt has grown significantly over the
OL,13,Fyears, leading to a summer race being
OL,14,Fintroduced in 2017 - with events now
OL,15,Fknown as the Winter Spine Race and
OL,16,FSummer Spine Race.
OL,18,FThis year, the winter competition
OL,19,Fstarted on the 11th of January and is
OL,20,Fdue to finish on the 18th of January.
