OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,FThe non-stop race along the Pennine
OL,7,FWay spans stretches of the Peak
OL,8,FDistrict, the Yorkshire Dales,
OL,9,FNorthumberland National Park,
OL,10,FHadrian's Wall and the Cheviots - and
OL,11,Fit is as much of a mental challenge as
OL,12,Fit is a physical one.
OL,14,FThe total ascent is more than 10
OL,15,Fthousand metres - and those competing
OL,16,Fwill contend with temperatures
OL,17,Fpredicted to be as low as -10C, as
OL,18,Fwell as snowy conditions and harsh
OL,19,Fwinds.
