OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,FLucy Gossage, an oncologist and former
OL,7,Fpro triathlete, won the woman's
OL,8,FMontane Winter Spine Race in January
OL,9,F2025.
OL,11,FSpeaking from Nottingham City Hospital
OL,12,Fwhere she works, Lucy told ITV News
OL,13,Fthat, although she was happy with her
OL,14,Fdecision not to take part this year,
OL,15,Fshe did envy those on the start line.
OL,17,F"I was watching some of it yesterday
OL,18,Fand over the weekend and it really
OL,19,Fmade me realise how bonkers it is,"
OL,20,Fshe said.
