OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,F"When you're doing it you just kind of
OL,7,Fnormalise it. I ran chunks and I'd
OL,8,Fthink 'that was a decent run' but
OL,9,Factually it wasn't even 3% of the
OL,10,Fwhole thing! So yeah, it really
OL,11,Femphasised for me just how crazy the
OL,12,Fwhole experience is."
OL,14,FLucy says the route through Cumbria
OL,15,Fand the Borders is one of her
OL,16,Ffavourite sections of the race -
OL,17,Fdespite how exhausted she was when she
OL,18,Freached it.
