OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,F"You come out of Alston and there's a
OL,7,Freally tough bit across fields and
OL,8,Fit's quite tricky to navigate - for me
OL,9,Fthat was in the middle of the night.
OL,10,FBut then you're on Hadrian's Wall.
OL,11,FIt's tough but it's amazing. I was
OL,12,Fthere in the pitch black and it's just
OL,13,Fso beautiful.
OL,15,F"And you go through the woods Kielder
OL,16,Fand the bit over the Cheviots is
OL,17,Fincredible. It's absolutely beautiful
OL,18,Fbut you're so exhausted by that point.
