OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,F"I remember the sun was setting and I
OL,7,Fremember stopping and taking a video
OL,8,Fknowing that would be my last sunset
OL,9,Fand this clear sky with all of the
OL,10,Fstars and the moon. It's experiences
OL,11,Flike that that make it so magical.
OL,13,F"Your brain empties of everything else
OL,14,Fthat is relevant and important and
OL,15,Fyou're just so immersed in the race
OL,16,Fand survival. That part of the Pennine
OL,17,FWay is probably one of my favourites,"
OL,18,Fshe added.
