OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,FAs well as the full 268-mile route,
OL,7,Fthe Winter Spine event also features
OL,8,Fsix other races of different distances
OL,9,Fand paces.
OL,11,FSarah Perry, from Cockermouth, won the
OL,12,FMRT Challenger South Race - a route
OL,13,Fthat is open to Mountain Rescue team
OL,14,Fmembers and involves a 108-mile race
OL,15,Falong the southern section of the
OL,16,FPennine Way.
OL,18,FSarah completed the route in 31 hours
OL,19,Fand 37 minutes.
