OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,FHer win comes just five weeks after
OL,7,FSarah claimed victory at The Hill - 56
OL,8,Flaps up and down The Wrekin in
OL,9,FShropshire - and only 11 weeks after
OL,10,Fshe achieved a world record at
OL,11,FBackyard Ultra in Tennessee.
OL,13,FThose completing the full 268-mile
OL,14,Ftrail will be battling through icy
OL,15,Fconditions and mental limits to reach
OL,16,Fthe finish line in the Borders this
OL,17,Fweek - but Lucy says the satisfaction
OL,18,Fof completing the race doesn't sink in
OL,19,Funtil some time after crossing it.
