OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,FShe says taking part in the Spine
OL,7,Fchanged her life in more ways than she
OL,8,Fcould never have imagined - and she is
OL,9,Fencouraging others to challenge
OL,10,Fthemselves.
OL,12,F"I always think if anyone is thinking
OL,13,For has got something that they're not
OL,14,Fquite sure if they're ready for it or
OL,15,Fit scares them, sometimes you just
OL,16,Fneed to press go and put yourself out
OL,17,Fthere.
