OL,3,C'If you're pondering press go', says
OL,4,Cformer Winter Spine Race winner
OL,6,F"Adventures like the Spine they do
OL,7,Fchange your life, even if you're not
OL,8,Fquite sure how they will do but they
OL,9,Fdo change your life. I realised it
OL,10,Fgives me so much confidence to go out
OL,11,Fand do crazy stuff and that will never
OL,12,Fever be taken away. So, yeah, if
OL,13,Fyou're pondering press go!"
